tightening effect on slope."}, {"tag": "positioning", "text": "Crowded flattener positioning could amplify a snapback if data surprises hawkish-to-dovish."}], "trade": {"legs": [{"instrument": "DGS2", "weight": 0.5}, {"instrument": "DGS10", "weight": -0.5}], "conviction": 0.45, "rationale": "Flattener: long front-end yield exposure, short long-end yield exposure, expressing continued 2s10s compression per direct spread measurement and labor-market corroboration."}}

